From Jeff W Boote Subject Re Mwm title drag crashes X server SIGPIPE In article , S Ramakrishnan writes Environment mach arch sparc sun IPX OS SunOS X X R patchlevel Motif I bring up X server using 'startx' and usr bin X Xsun The following sequence of actions crashes the X server SIGPIPE, errno , 'xinit' reports that connexion to X server lost I had this problem as well It had to do with the CG graphics card that comes with the IPX What fixed the problem for me was to apply the sunGX uu that was part of Patch Patch also used this file so perhaps you didn't apply the one that came with Patch jeff Jeff W Boote Scientific Computing Division There is nothing good or bad National Center for Atmospheric Research but thinking makes it so Boulder Hamlet